OL,5, The Nigerian army has arrested two     
OL,6, soldiers after a viral video allegedly 
OL,7, showed them torturing a civilian.      
OL,9,FIn the footage, a man in military      
OL,10,Ffatigues and another in civilian       
OL,11,Fclothing repeatedly kick and whip a    
OL,12,Fthird shirtless man, as he repeatedly  
OL,13,Fpleas for mercy.                       
OL,15,F"No, no sir, abeg! (I beg). I will     
OL,16,Fconfess sir, abeg!" the man cries out. 
OL,18,FThe army has expressed "utmost dismay" 
OL,19,Fat the "unprofessional conduct"        
OL,20,Fallegedly displayed by the officers.   
